  m_text: 'Work to revitalize joy and life in sick and injured individuals, changing
    not just lives, but the world, for the better.

    Work with patients on both
    a physical and emotional level, helping them through their troubles, remedying
    what ails them, and allowing them to live happily with their family oncemore. '
